skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
des: The Community Development Foundation is the local chamber of commerce for Tupelo, Mississippi and is the economic development organization for Lee county, Mississippi. CDF uses Amazon Alexa to keep our members engaged with chamber events and announcements concerning the economic growth of Tupelo and Lee County, Mississippi. With the CDF skill with Amazon Alexa you can keep up to date with what’s going on in the Chamber and be the first to receive exciting news of new business, industries and jobs in the Tupelo and Lee County, Mississippi area.
